    <title>Uncertainty-Aware Routing for
  Cost-Efficient LLM Inference</title>
    <summary>We propose an uncertainty-aware routing strategy that dispatches
  queries to models of different sizes based on predictive entropy, reducing
  inference cost by 30% while retaining 99% of quality.</summary>
